	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Fellow Magi!<br><br>Hail and sorrowfilled day!<br><br>Verant announced that they nerfed our only summons of value to our class, the Sword of Runes. They also nerfed the pet's dexterity in such a manner as to seriously affect teh survivability of our favorite summoned friends/enemies! Along with these nerfs they also nerfed CoH.<br><br>Our Epic Quest is still inordinately difficult in comparison to most other classes. <br><br>We've little or no recourse with Verant to let them know our disatisfaction with their current decisions regarding our class,short of canceling our accounts. Many have already stated on various boards that they are going to be doing just that. <br><br>Instead of canceling your account I suggest that all Magi, across all servers unanimously boycott the Magi Best of the Best.The reason for this recommendation is: We have to show Verant that enough is enough! We have to show them that their nerfing our class and impacting us in such a negative manner is intolerable and that we are tired of their actions. <br><br>If everyone is prepaired to do this, I suggest the following: Everyone log in your Magi, and proceed to the Arena, BUT, have a seat, and not participate in the event. When asked why, simply state that you are demonstrating against Verant's lack of concern over this, our Chosen Class and the nerfs Verant has insulted us with!<br><br>Remember folks, the winner of the Best of the Best competitions are getting nothing more then a title. They haven't got any new, great item so if the lack of isn't that big of a deal to you, but the nerfs and their impact to your playing is, here's a possible solution!<br><br>Elrique Melnebone<br>Magi of the 13th Spell Circle (51)<br>Veeshan<br>&nbsp;<br>Elrique Melnebone<br>Elementalist of Blood and Honor<br>Master Vending Machine<br>Veeshan</td></tr>
