	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi there!<br><br>Equiptment.  I've found it's not as important to us at lower levels then to other classes.  I'm still wearing the same cloth armor now as I was 17 levels ago.  But some things that you should have or be looking for might be a pair of +2 INT rings (buy them from other players, expect 2-4pp each), a Skull of Jhen'tra (adds 20 mana, goes around 10-15pp), and maybe a Water Crystal Staff, but thats not too important.<br><br>In the not-too-distant future I'd be looking toward a Flowing Black Robe and a Savant's Cap, and you'll be right where I am at 17th, looking for money! (Shovel of Ponz quest is expencive)<br><br>You're spells and pet are your most valuable equiptment, but these can sure help.<br><br>Best of luck,<br>Zemplokazo, Karana server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
