	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm a 51 mage and have found that with most mobs the water pet is the best to use. I can solo 5 to 7 hg's before I have to let the pet heal.  Then the down time is low because of the high regen of the water pet. I have also been accused of my water pet rooting mobs because they have the best taunt of any of the pets. So when I have the chance to use the water pet when soloing I do. Fire and Air are the best for when in groups. But in places like Kanors the earth pet is the only choice because of the runners. So keep in mind it all depends on what/where and how your fighting to determin what pet to use.  Example I was in 1 group in kanors with 4 mages, 1 cleric, and 1 warrior. We had 2 air and 1 fire and 1 earth pet, hunted for hours no runners and the cleric didn't have to cast many complete heals with the stuns from the air pets.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
