	   <tr><td colspan=2>I was soloing saplings and greenwoods at level 21.  The only real problem I had was finding enough at the right level for me to take out.  If you do want to fight them, damage shield your pet and send him in then back up and use your bolt of flame spell from as far back as you can.  You may need to run around a bit if they aggro on you, so having the extra space to see them coming is a good thing.  They are exellent xp and loot though, diffinetly worth the effort.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
